OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Fovernight with clear spells.
OL,7,FTemperatures falling to give a risk of
OL,8,Ffrost, especially in the west. Low
OL,9,Fcloud moving into eastern parts, with
OL,10,Fareas of mist and fog developing for
OL,11,Fmany overnight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FA dry and sunny day expected
OL,14,Fonce early low cloud, mist and fog
OL,15,Fclears. Sunshine may be a little hazy
OL,16,Fat times. Warm for most, but cooler
OL,17,Fnear coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
